### Address Details Endpoint

This endpoint allows you to create a new address entry.

#### Request Body

- `address_type` (string): Type of address, e.g. "work".

- `address_1` (string): First line of the address, e.g. "456 Avenue".

- `address_2` (string): Second line of the address, e.g. "Suite 5B".

- `street` (string): Street name, e.g. "Main Blvd".

- `city` (string): City name, e.g. "CityB".

- `state_name` (string): State name, e.g. "StateB".

- `country` (string): Country name, e.g. "CountryB".

- `postal_zip_code` (string): Postal or zip code, e.g. "123456".

- `google_address` (string): Google address information.

- `is_primary` (boolean): Indicates if the address is primary.


#### Response

The response for this request follows the JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "address_id": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

